8%200%2018-2l1-2v3l84%201h84v-5H16v3m240%200v2h144v-5H257l-1%203m-94%2010v1c1%200%202%202%202%207l1%209c0%202-3%202-60%202H44v6l61-1h60v3c0%203%200%203-2%202h-2l2%204%201%204H44v23l1%2023%201-2c0-2%206-2%208-1v3l2-2c0-1%201-2%202-1l2%202%201%201%201-2%209-2c11%200%2012%201%2012%203l1%201%201-2a921%20921%200%2000161%202h154v-45l-115-1-114-1v-7c-2%202-3%201-3-2v-3h232v-5H168l-1-9v-9c2-1-2-2-5-1\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lightworks replace edit\"\n        title=\"lightworks replace edit\"\n        src=\"/static/291bc9ec2c0906b68744ea7f0172d827/36dbb/Selection_005.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/291bc9ec2c0906b68744ea7f0172d827/f06cd/Selection_005.jpg 240w,\n/static/291bc9ec2c0906b68744ea7f0172d827/a5e48/Selection_005.jpg 480w,\n/static/291bc9ec2c0906b68744ea7f0172d827/36dbb/Selection_005.jpg 700w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Awesome, your first edit! Unfortunately, if you followed my lead, then you’ve made a horrible mistake! There’s a bit of a blooper somewhere near the end of this take. Unique ID seems to lose his balance, and then Adelie… well, I don’t know what Adelie is doing.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 699px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'267\\'%20viewBox=\\'0%200%20400%20267\\'%20preserveAspectRatio=\\'none\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M1%201L0%20134v13